-- table to hook into, so this builds its own small panel matching the hub's look. Ported
-- from the old hub's MM2 page: Coin Farm, Auto Gun (pickup), Auto Stab, Auto Shoot, and
-- Murderer/Sheriff role detection + ESP. The old hub's ThemeObjects/HubState wiring,
-- rebindable keybinds, remote-based role clues (SetMurderer/SetSheriff/round-data polling),
-- and the PC-gui mobile-control repair pass were all dropped -- this panel doesn't have
-- that shared plumbing, and tool-based role detection (who's holding the Knife/Gun) alone
-- covers the same need. Role highlighting is automatic now (no manual ESP toggle) -- as
-- soon as a murderer/sheriff is detected, they're highlighted; the Murderer/Sheriff avatar
-- + name reveal lives in its own popup (Role Reveal button) instead of always on the panel.
